    "**No Real-Time Data Access** -I was trained on data up to **2024**, so I don't have access to real-time market prices, interest rates, or breaking financial news (e.g., today's stock movements or sudden central bank decisions).",
    "-Example: I can explain how a Fed rate hike typically affects mortgage rates, but I can't tell you the current 30-year fixed mortgage rate.",
    "**No Personalization Without Context** -I don't know your personal financial situation unless you tell me --things like income, debts, risk tolerance, time horizon, or tax bracket.",
    "-While I can offer general principles (e.g., \"diversify your portfolio\"), truly personalized advice requires a licensed advisor who can assess your full picture and fiduciary needs.",
    "**No Legal or Regulatory Authority** -I'm not a licensed financial advisor, broker, accountant, or attorney."
